## 📶 1. WiFi and Hotspot Connecting Methods

https://support.microsoft.com/images/en-us/c25f0805-21af-4863-846d-d414961f94ef

https://support.microsoft.com/images/en-us/d0319ef0-bc6d-4f1c-a8cf-8ccdeeeba9e6

### Connecting to WiFi:

- Click the **Network icon** in the taskbar
- Select available network
- Enter password → Connect

### Using Command Prompt:

```
netsh wlan show profiles
netsh wlan connectname="WiFi_Name"
```

### Creating a Hotspot:

- Go to **Settings → Network & Internet → Mobile Hotspot**
- Share internet via WiFi or Ethernet
- Turn ON hotspot

